OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1780143067
OL,3,CPredator who sexually assaulted
OL,4,Csleeping women on night Tubes is jailed
OL,6,FA predator who sexually assaulted a
OL,7,Fstring of women who had fallen asleep
OL,8,Fon night Tubes was finally caught
OL,9,Fafter being jailed for another crime.
OL,11,FSalman Yousaf, 46, was already in
OL,12,Fprison in 2024 when the Metropolitan
OL,13,FPolice tipped off British Transport
OL,14,FPolice (BTP) about his identity and
OL,15,Fmethod of offending.
OL,17,FBTP then went back through records of
OL,18,Fcrimes where no suspect had been
OL,19,Fidentified and discovered he had
OL,20,Fcommitted a series of sexual assaults
OL,21,Fbetween 2017 and 2021.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
