FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1780143067
OL,3,CPredator who sexually assaulted
OL,4,Csleeping women on night Tubes is jailed
OL,6,FHe admitted eight counts of sexual
OL,7,Fassault and one of outraging public
OL,8,Fdecency, and was jailed at Inner
OL,9,FLondon Crown Court, where he was also
OL,10,Ftold he will spend an additional four
OL,11,Fyears on licence after release.
OL,13,FYousaf was also placed on the sexual
OL,14,Foffenders register for life and placed
OL,15,Funder a sexual harm prevention order.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
