OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1780143067
OL,3,CPredator who sexually assaulted
OL,4,Csleeping women on night Tubes is jailed
OL,6,FBTP said investigators had not managed
OL,7,Fto identify him earlier because of a
OL,8,Flack of on-train CCTV footage and the
OL,9,Ffact he had not swiped in or out at
OL,10,Fticket barriers when several of the
OL,11,Foffences were committed.
OL,13,FHis first crime was around 5am on
OL,14,FMarch 11 2017 when he performed a sex
OL,15,Fact in front of a woman on a Central
OL,16,FLine service near Stratford.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
