PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1780143067
OL,3,CPredator who sexually assaulted
OL,4,Csleeping women on night Tubes is jailed
OL,6,FYousaf went on to sexually assault
OL,7,Fanother eight women on Central and
OL,8,FJubilee line services, singling out
OL,9,Fthose who were on their own and had
OL,10,Ffallen asleep on night Tubes.
OL,12,FBTP Detective Constable Iryna Cuthbert
OL,13,Fsaid: "Salman Yousaf is a calculated
OL,14,Fpredator who deliberately exploited
OL,15,Fthe night-time rail network to target
OL,16,Flone women, using their isolation to
OL,17,Fcommit a series of premeditated crimes.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1780143067
OL,3,CPredator who sexually assaulted
OL,4,Csleeping women on night Tubes is jailed
OL,6,F"Even when confronted, he showed a
OL,7,Fcomplete lack of remorse ` the same
OL,8,Fabsence of remorse he demonstrated at
OL,9,Fhis sentencing.
OL,11,F"Thanks to the information provided by
OL,12,Four colleagues at the Metropolitan
OL,13,FPolice, we were able to link him to a
OL,14,Fcatalogue of vile sexual offending and
OL,15,Fultimately extend his stay behind bars
OL,16,Fbeyond 2030.
OL,18,F"Yousaf's crimes will have a lasting
OL,19,Fimpact on the women he targeted.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1780143067
OL,3,CPredator who sexually assaulted
OL,4,Csleeping women on night Tubes is jailed
OL,6,F"I want to acknowledge their bravery
OL,7,Fin coming forward and reporting what
OL,8,Fhappened, and I hope his sentence
OL,9,Fbrings them some measure of justice."
OL,11,FYousaf was serving a prison term after
OL,12,Ftargeting another woman who had fallen
OL,13,Fasleep on the Tube, leading her away
OL,14,Ffrom the station and sexually
OL,15,Fassaulting her in a road near West Ham
OL,16,Fstation.
OL,18,FHe was jailed for seven and a half
OL,19,Fyears after a trial at Snaresbrook
OL,20,FCrown Court for sexual assault and
OL,21,Fsexual assault by penetration.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
