PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1780143067
OL,3,CPredator who sexually assaulted
OL,4,Csleeping women on night Tubes is jailed
OL,6,FMet detectives tracked CCTV from the
OL,7,Fnight of the attack, piecing together
OL,8,FYousaf's movements and discovering he
OL,9,Ffrequently used Forest Gate station.
OL,11,FThey spoke to staff there and
OL,12,Fidentified him, leading to his arrest.
